{"books":[{"id":"rmrb","name":"人民日报","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"","files":[],"article":{"title":"焊花飞溅报春来","authors":["居有松"],"dates":[{"year":1967,"month":12,"day":1}],"is_range_date":false,"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"焊花飞溅报春来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沪东造船厂工人　居有松"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挂红灯啊扎彩牌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"快把毛主席巨像挂起来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"宽阔船台是会场啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蓝天万里幕拉开。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一条条新船高昂首，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一面面红旗两边排，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"造船厂里人沸腾，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喜报铺天盖地来。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"元旦开个庆功会，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人如山啊情似海，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"畅谈文化革命形势无限好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁不想跳上台来摆一摆。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"胜利的战果说不完，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"歌声笑语传天外，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国赫鲁晓夫被打倒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"资产阶级司令部垮了台！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"站在船台看世界，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命洪流排山倒海，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“枪杆子里面出政权”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把帝修反脚下踩。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山常青啊水常绿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"世界人民无限热爱毛主席，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东思想照全球，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永放光彩红万代。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“抓革命，促生产”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"焊花飞溅报春来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"共产主义巨轮咱们造，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席掌舵把路开。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"庆功的会啊战斗的会，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战歌阵阵抒胸怀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"紧紧跟着毛主席，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铁锤打出新世界。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":1,"page_end":1,"alias":""},"tags":[{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}